p: Linalool, caryophyllene, dibutyl phthalate, (-)-4-terpineol, and (-)- α-terpineol are the most important active ingredients which have the highest degree in Compound Anshen essential oil. The systemsDock website database was used to verify the molecular docking of the main medicinal ingredients and proteins. In brief, the systemsDock website database was logged into; the target name was uploaded, which included linalool, caryophyllene, dibutyl phthalate, (-)-4-terpineol, and (-)- α-terpineol in.sdf format; and the 3D structure and docking were analyzed.
